1
00:00:49,299 --> 00:00:51,968
STILL SHINING

2
00:01:06,399 --> 00:01:08,234
Mesti dah tengok bilik peperiksaan.

3
00:01:08,318 --> 00:01:09,444
Ada jam di dinding?

4
00:01:09,527 --> 00:01:10,445
Tak ada.

5
00:01:11,237 --> 00:01:13,448
Mesti mereka akan beritahu masa,

6
00:01:13,531 --> 00:01:15,742
tapi bawa sajalah jam, mana tahu.

7
00:01:15,825 --> 00:01:19,204
Esok cikgu jemput pukul 7.00 pagi,
tunggu di hentian bas.

8
00:01:19,287 --> 00:01:21,664
- Jangan lambat.
- Okey.

9
00:01:23,083 --> 00:01:24,334
Tidur awal,

10
00:01:24,417 --> 00:01:27,087
makan sarapan esok,
jangan lupa bawa bekal.

11
00:01:27,170 --> 00:01:29,464
Slip ID peperiksaan. Itu penting.

12
00:01:29,547 --> 00:01:30,548
- Baiklah.
- Okey.

13
00:01:31,841 --> 00:01:33,426
- Tidur lena.
- Baiklah.

14
00:01:39,933 --> 00:01:40,850
Helo?

15
00:01:44,354 --> 00:01:46,564
Itu…

16
00:01:47,148 --> 00:01:48,942
Kertas kerja?

17
00:01:49,859 --> 00:01:51,945
<i>Kita jumpa pukul 6.50 pagi esok.</i>

18
00:01:52,028 --> 00:01:53,363
Masuk dalam bilik…

19
00:01:53,947 --> 00:01:55,281
Laci kedua di kanan.

20
00:01:55,365 --> 00:01:56,741
<i>Okey, tidur lena.</i>

21
00:01:57,408 --> 00:01:58,868
Ada, bukan? Dah kata.

22
00:01:58,952 --> 00:02:00,787
Okey, saya tahulah.

23
00:02:01,371 --> 00:02:03,123
Okey.

24
00:02:10,463 --> 00:02:11,756
Kenapa keluar dulu?

25
00:02:11,840 --> 00:02:13,508
Helo, cikgu.

26
00:02:14,050 --> 00:02:16,052
Banyak cikgu tolong dia

27
00:02:16,136 --> 00:02:18,763
sampai ke hari sebelum peperiksaan.

28
00:02:18,847 --> 00:02:21,266
- Susah-susah saja.
- Tak susah pun.

29
00:02:21,349 --> 00:02:22,642
Saya ikhlas.

30
00:02:24,269 --> 00:02:28,231
Pak cik, Tae-seo perlukan jam tangan,
tapi jam saya jam digital.

31
00:02:28,314 --> 00:02:29,482
Ada jam analog?

32
00:02:30,733 --> 00:02:33,027
Jam ini usianya lebih 40 tahun.

33
00:02:33,111 --> 00:02:34,445
Asalkan bergerak saja.

34
00:02:35,822 --> 00:02:36,781
Yakah?

35
00:02:38,449 --> 00:02:39,576
Hulur tangan kamu.

36
00:02:40,326 --> 00:02:41,286
Pakai sekarang,

37
00:02:41,369 --> 00:02:42,412
supaya tak lupa.

38
00:02:50,753 --> 00:02:53,214
Pak cik dan mak cik jaga dia dengan baik.

39
00:02:54,382 --> 00:02:56,009
Cikgu pun sama.

40
00:03:47,894 --> 00:03:48,937
<i>Awak tidur lena?</i>

41
00:03:49,020 --> 00:03:51,272
Ya, sangat lena.

42
00:03:51,356 --> 00:03:52,982
Saya ingatkan saya resah.

43
00:03:53,566 --> 00:03:56,402
Saya tahu awak akan duduki peperiksaan
di bilik sebelah,

44
00:03:56,486 --> 00:03:57,695
saya jadi tenang.

45
00:04:00,782 --> 00:04:02,909
Lama awak tunggu? Mesti awak sejuk.

46
00:04:03,785 --> 00:04:04,744
Panas.

47
00:04:04,827 --> 00:04:07,413
Ayah kata hari peperiksaan
selalunya sejuk di Korea.

48
00:04:10,166 --> 00:04:11,084
Biar saya pakai.

49
00:04:20,802 --> 00:04:21,844
Begini?

50
00:04:21,928 --> 00:04:22,762
Bukan.

51
00:04:26,474 --> 00:04:29,310
Pusing,

52
00:04:30,979 --> 00:04:32,188
kemudian ikat.

53
00:04:42,282 --> 00:04:45,410
Saya nak masuk kolej
paling dekat dengan awak.

54
00:04:46,286 --> 00:04:48,830
Kalau tak dapat di Seoul,
dekat Seoul pun jadi.

55
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:55,086
Tolong kami capai impian kami hari ini.

56
00:04:57,005 --> 00:04:58,006
Saya rasa

57
00:04:58,715 --> 00:05:00,300
mafela ini akan bantu saya.

58
00:05:01,467 --> 00:05:02,635
Beri saya sesuatu.

59
00:05:02,719 --> 00:05:03,636
Apa-apa awak punya.

60
00:05:13,021 --> 00:05:13,855
Ada.

61
00:05:16,441 --> 00:05:18,568
SEKOLAH TINGGI YEONWOO
YEON TAE-SEO

62
00:05:19,193 --> 00:05:20,028
Tangkal tuah.

63
00:05:22,488 --> 00:05:26,034
BILIK PEPERIKSAAN 6

64
00:05:44,385 --> 00:05:50,308
STILL SHINING

65
00:05:51,684 --> 00:05:54,353
Peperiksaan dah habis!

66
00:05:57,607 --> 00:05:58,608
Saya saja gembira?

67
00:06:02,737 --> 00:06:03,613
Dah habis!

68
00:06:07,116 --> 00:06:09,410
Tae-seo, jom kita tengok Sungai Hangang.

69
00:06:09,494 --> 00:06:11,287
Kita dah tengok pantai, jom ke sana.

70
00:06:11,954 --> 00:06:13,039
Tapi dah pukul…

71
00:06:13,122 --> 00:06:14,248
Jomlah. Sempat.

72
00:06:15,750 --> 00:06:16,793
Sekejap.

73
00:06:24,842 --> 00:06:25,927
Ada 7,000 won.

74
00:06:26,469 --> 00:06:27,386
Lain kalilah.

75
00:06:32,183 --> 00:06:34,435
Saya tak guna duit sejak dengan awak.

76
00:06:34,519 --> 00:06:36,771
Awak dah bantu saya simpan,
biar saya belanja.

77
00:06:36,854 --> 00:06:38,356
Jom naik kereta api.

78
00:06:46,364 --> 00:06:47,615
Tak payah kereta api.

79
00:06:58,042 --> 00:07:00,169
Kita tengok dari Terminal Bas Dongseoul.

80
00:07:00,253 --> 00:07:01,462
Nampak dari sana?

81
00:07:01,546 --> 00:07:03,840
Ya, Sungai Hangang dekat Stesen Gangbyeon.

82
00:07:05,049 --> 00:07:07,301
Kita tengok sungai,
pergi dari Stesen Gangbyeon,

83
00:07:07,385 --> 00:07:10,555
ambil kereta api terakhir
dari Cheongyangni, sampai esok pagi.

84
00:07:10,638 --> 00:07:12,014
Kenapa balik naik kereta api?

85
00:07:12,557 --> 00:07:15,393
Sebab kereta api ambil masa enam jam,

86
00:07:18,062 --> 00:07:21,357
jadi kita boleh bersama lama sikit.

87
00:07:23,484 --> 00:07:24,360
Bijak.

88
00:07:27,738 --> 00:07:29,699
Boleh buat apa dengan 7,000 won?

89
00:07:31,409 --> 00:07:32,827
Belanja mi di bar khemah.

90
00:07:32,910 --> 00:07:35,413
Ayah kata mi di bar khemah Seoul sedap.

91
00:07:36,706 --> 00:07:37,540
Okey.

92
00:07:49,302 --> 00:07:50,887
- Nak pergi sana?
- Okey.

93
00:07:52,430 --> 00:07:53,764
Mi dah siap.

94
00:07:53,848 --> 00:07:55,016
- Terima kasih.
- Terima kasih.

95
00:08:03,483 --> 00:08:04,942
Biasa makan, tapi sedap.

96
00:08:09,989 --> 00:08:11,866
Saya sangat suka mi.

97
00:08:11,949 --> 00:08:13,868
Ayah saya selalu cakap,

98
00:08:13,951 --> 00:08:15,495
waktu mak kandungkan saya,

99
00:08:15,578 --> 00:08:17,121
dia mengidam mi bar khemah.

100
00:08:17,663 --> 00:08:19,790
Saya tertanya-tanya apa rasanya.

101
00:08:25,463 --> 00:08:26,672
Saya tahulah.

102
00:08:26,756 --> 00:08:28,966
Saya selalu cakap pasal mak
kalau ke Seoul.

103
00:08:29,050 --> 00:08:30,259
Tapi saya tak rindu.

104
00:08:33,596 --> 00:08:34,430
Dia di sini?

105
00:08:35,723 --> 00:08:36,849
Di luar negara.

106
00:08:37,850 --> 00:08:39,143
Tapi tak tahu di mana.

107
00:08:39,227 --> 00:08:40,561
Saya tak pernah tanya.

108
00:08:42,230 --> 00:08:44,065
Mesti dia hidup baik-baik saja.

109
00:08:45,566 --> 00:08:47,693
Di tempat yang tak ada kaitan dengan saya.

110
00:08:52,532 --> 00:08:54,575
Kita boleh naik kereta api pukul 10.00.

111
00:08:55,701 --> 00:08:56,953
Sungai Hangang pula?

112
00:08:57,995 --> 00:08:59,580
Tengok dari stesen.

113
00:08:59,664 --> 00:09:00,957
Tak nak dari stesen.

114
00:09:01,040 --> 00:09:02,833
Nak tengok dekat-dekat.

115
00:09:07,713 --> 00:09:08,631
Makan cepat.

116
00:09:15,805 --> 00:09:17,848
Sungai Hangang di depan mata saya.

117
00:09:17,932 --> 00:09:18,933
Kali pertama tengok.

118
00:09:19,016 --> 00:09:19,892
Saya pun.

119
00:09:20,685 --> 00:09:22,353
- Jom pergi dekat.
- Nanti.

120
00:09:24,814 --> 00:09:25,856
Awak…

121
00:09:26,607 --> 00:09:27,525
mesti sejuk.

122
00:09:29,402 --> 00:09:30,319
Pusing…

123
00:09:31,988 --> 00:09:32,989
pusing,

124
00:09:33,573 --> 00:09:34,448
kemudian ikat.

125
00:09:37,910 --> 00:09:39,870
Awak pula? Tak sejuk?

126
00:09:39,954 --> 00:09:40,788
Saya boleh…

127
00:09:42,707 --> 00:09:43,666
pakai ini.

128
00:09:57,513 --> 00:09:58,556
Ini hari bersejarah.

129
00:09:58,639 --> 00:10:00,600
Saya tengok pantai dan Sungai Hangang.

130
00:10:01,851 --> 00:10:03,311
Saya kena ingat hari ini.

131
00:10:10,443 --> 00:10:11,277
Yeon Tae-seo.

132
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:13,404
Saya dah ada impian.

133
00:10:13,487 --> 00:10:14,447
Nak tinggal sendiri.

134
00:10:15,072 --> 00:10:16,407
Jauh daripada ayah.

135
00:10:16,490 --> 00:10:18,993
Ini dianggap satu mimpi

136
00:10:19,076 --> 00:10:21,495
sebab itu hanya mungkin kalau ayah sihat.

137
00:10:21,579 --> 00:10:23,998
Kalau ayah tak sihat, jangan haraplah.

138
00:10:24,081 --> 00:10:27,460
Impian saya agar ayah sihat
supaya saya boleh berdikari.

139
00:10:29,462 --> 00:10:30,296
Awak pula?

140
00:10:31,380 --> 00:10:32,381
Saya?

141
00:10:33,132 --> 00:10:34,258
Impian saya…

142
00:10:37,178 --> 00:10:39,388
Kalau awak nak berdikari,
saya nak harapkan diri.

143
00:10:40,056 --> 00:10:41,307
Tak ada "daripada".

144
00:10:42,725 --> 00:10:44,060
Itu sangat hebat.

145
00:10:44,810 --> 00:10:45,645
Maksud awak?

146
00:10:45,728 --> 00:10:48,898
Sebab saya tahu
awak akan capai dengan mudah.

147
00:10:49,482 --> 00:10:52,234
Apa yang saya nampak,
awak boleh buat semua benda sendiri.

148
00:10:53,819 --> 00:10:55,696
- Yakah?
- Ya.

149
00:10:55,780 --> 00:10:57,615
Saya tak suka buat apa-apa sendiri,

150
00:10:57,698 --> 00:10:59,158
tapi awak memang pandai.

151
00:10:59,241 --> 00:11:01,786
Saya tak pernah tengok
awak melepak dengan sesiapa.

152
00:11:02,370 --> 00:11:03,663
Pandai bawa diri.

153
00:11:04,288 --> 00:11:05,498
Sangat hebat.

154
00:11:06,957 --> 00:11:08,084
Tapi yalah,

155
00:11:08,167 --> 00:11:10,461
mesti lain lepas awak masuk universiti.

156
00:11:12,088 --> 00:11:14,632
Apa lagi yang akan berubah tentang awak?

157
00:11:16,676 --> 00:11:18,511
Saya rasa tak ada apa-apa.

158
00:11:23,099 --> 00:11:24,100
Nak pergi jauh sikit?

159
00:11:25,851 --> 00:11:27,728
Nak. Kita ada masa?

160
00:11:31,774 --> 00:11:33,484
Tak ada.

161
00:11:35,778 --> 00:11:36,612
Jom.

162
00:11:37,696 --> 00:11:38,531
Kita kena pergi.

163
00:11:38,614 --> 00:11:39,907
Jom, nanti lambat.

164
00:11:52,002 --> 00:11:53,838
Jauh kita berjalan nak tengok sungai.

165
00:11:57,174 --> 00:11:58,175
Sekejap.

166
00:11:59,301 --> 00:12:00,302
Aduh, penatnya.

167
00:12:00,845 --> 00:12:02,012
Kalori mi dah habis.

168
00:12:05,433 --> 00:12:06,600
Kita dah lambat.

169
00:12:10,229 --> 00:12:11,230
Jom.

170
00:12:17,319 --> 00:12:18,320
Lari.

171
00:12:43,262 --> 00:12:46,807
<i>Di hentian bas pagi tadi,</i>

172
00:12:47,349 --> 00:12:48,851
<i>saya tengok awak sampai.</i>

173
00:13:07,036 --> 00:13:08,579
<i>Kita akan di mana,</i>

174
00:13:09,497 --> 00:13:10,539
<i>kita buat apa</i>

175
00:13:11,332 --> 00:13:12,458
<i>dan dengan siapa.</i>

176
00:13:14,001 --> 00:13:17,880
<i>Yang mana antara tiga itu</i>
<i>akan ditentukan lepas peperiksaan nanti.</i>

177
00:13:20,090 --> 00:13:20,925
<i>Kemudian,</i>

178
00:13:21,717 --> 00:13:24,970
<i>adakah ini kali terakhir</i>

179
00:13:25,554 --> 00:13:27,014
<i>kita menuju</i>

180
00:13:28,641 --> 00:13:29,975
<i>ke arah yang sama?</i>

181
00:13:33,437 --> 00:13:35,064
Memang belum pasti,

182
00:13:35,981 --> 00:13:38,817
tapi mesti akan berubah
apabila kita di universiti berbeza.

183
00:13:40,611 --> 00:13:41,654
Tak.

184
00:13:42,363 --> 00:13:45,699
Jarak jadi masalah
ketika pesanan mesej tak wujud.

185
00:13:48,452 --> 00:13:50,538
Kalau masih boleh hantar mesej,

186
00:13:51,205 --> 00:13:52,414
semua jadi dekat.

187
00:13:53,332 --> 00:13:54,708
Boleh mesej dari jauh.

188
00:13:54,792 --> 00:13:56,085
Betul.

189
00:13:57,253 --> 00:13:59,171
Boleh mesej dari mana-mana.

190
00:13:59,255 --> 00:14:00,798
Sambungan di Yeonwoo pun bagus.

191
00:14:02,049 --> 00:14:05,761
Tempat terpencil di negara lain
tak boleh hantar mesejkah?

192
00:14:05,844 --> 00:14:07,596
Selagi bukan di dunia lain,

193
00:14:09,181 --> 00:14:10,391
semua tempat boleh.

194
00:14:11,976 --> 00:14:13,143
Dunia lain…

195
00:14:15,271 --> 00:14:16,522
Macam saya dan mak.

196
00:14:19,984 --> 00:14:20,859
Samalah.

197
00:14:25,072 --> 00:14:27,491
Ada yang hanya terpakai untuk kita

198
00:14:29,201 --> 00:14:30,536
sebab ini soal kita.

199
00:14:32,621 --> 00:14:37,501
Kita berdua akan cuba sedaya upaya
untuk luangkan masa bersama.

200
00:14:39,378 --> 00:14:41,171
Kita akan usahakan.

201
00:14:45,676 --> 00:14:47,678
Awak begitu sukakan saya?

202
00:14:49,054 --> 00:14:50,055
Mestilah.

203
00:14:50,639 --> 00:14:52,641
Kalau saya tak seyakin ini,

204
00:14:54,685 --> 00:14:56,061
saya takkan cuba pun.

205
00:14:57,354 --> 00:14:58,397
Walaupun tak ada

206
00:15:00,900 --> 00:15:03,986
ruang dalam hidup untuk suka orang,
tapi perasaan ini mekar.

207
00:16:48,465 --> 00:16:49,758
Saya nak dengan awak.

208
00:17:12,239 --> 00:17:13,782
- Nak masuk?
- Ya.

209
00:17:14,283 --> 00:17:15,284
Nak masuk?

210
00:18:05,459 --> 00:18:06,585
Saya pergi ke mana?

211
00:18:09,505 --> 00:18:10,589
Sana?

212
00:18:12,633 --> 00:18:13,467
Okey.

213
00:19:22,995 --> 00:19:24,788
Bilik awak cantik.

214
00:19:25,706 --> 00:19:26,665
Ya.

215
00:19:44,183 --> 00:19:45,017
Biar saya…

216
00:19:45,601 --> 00:19:47,019
Saya boleh buat.

217
00:20:58,173 --> 00:20:59,007
Sekejap.

218
00:21:35,002 --> 00:21:36,003
Maaf.

219
00:22:21,381 --> 00:22:22,466
Eun-a, dah balik?

220
00:22:30,807 --> 00:22:31,975
Ayah awak?

221
00:22:33,643 --> 00:22:34,728
Eun-a.

222
00:22:34,811 --> 00:22:36,271
Ya, ayah!

223
00:22:42,444 --> 00:22:43,612
Saya dah balik.

224
00:22:45,113 --> 00:22:46,656
Saya nak mandi, nak tidur.

225
00:22:46,740 --> 00:22:48,241
Esok kamu ke sekolah?

226
00:22:48,325 --> 00:22:49,868
Ya, tapi boleh pergi lambat.

227
00:22:51,453 --> 00:22:52,454
Selamat malam, ayah.

228
00:22:53,371 --> 00:22:54,748
Okey, syabas untuk hari ini.

229
00:22:55,290 --> 00:22:56,291
Kamu rehatlah.

230
00:22:57,084 --> 00:22:58,293
Ayah bangga dengan kamu.

231
00:22:59,127 --> 00:23:00,087
Terima kasih.

232
00:23:16,103 --> 00:23:17,062
Dia dah pergi?

233
00:23:56,226 --> 00:23:57,227
Jangan.

234
00:24:01,690 --> 00:24:04,276
Sebenarnya, saya ada rahsia besar.

235
00:24:06,278 --> 00:24:08,780
Saya malu nak beritahu awak.

236
00:24:25,005 --> 00:24:26,715
Saya panas, macam nak mati.

237
00:24:27,924 --> 00:24:30,218
Saya asyik fikir tentang baju panas.

238
00:24:30,302 --> 00:24:32,888
Hari ini tak sejuk sangat,
tapi ayah paksa.

239
00:24:35,390 --> 00:24:36,683
Malunya.

240
00:24:36,766 --> 00:24:39,019
Kenapa berbunga-bunga?

241
00:24:41,897 --> 00:24:42,981
Kenapa pula?

242
00:24:44,149 --> 00:24:45,358
Comellah.

243
00:25:36,785 --> 00:25:38,870
Awak memang sentiasa cemerlang,

244
00:25:38,954 --> 00:25:40,497
nanti kita fikir haluan awak.

245
00:25:40,580 --> 00:25:41,873
Fikir-fikirlah dulu.

246
00:25:41,957 --> 00:25:43,625
Okey. Terima kasih.

247
00:25:43,708 --> 00:25:44,668
Pergilah.

248
00:25:49,214 --> 00:25:50,340
Aduhai.

249
00:26:09,484 --> 00:26:11,861
Mo Eun-a, syabas. Bagus.

250
00:26:12,821 --> 00:26:13,655
Terima kasih.

251
00:26:14,614 --> 00:26:18,159
Keputusan awak boleh tahan
walaupun baru rajin setengah tahun.

252
00:26:19,160 --> 00:26:19,995
Betul.

253
00:26:20,495 --> 00:26:22,163
Kalaulah awak mula setahun awal,

254
00:26:23,081 --> 00:26:25,000
kita boleh cuba laluan kemasukan wilayah.

255
00:26:25,583 --> 00:26:26,584
Sayangnya.

256
00:26:28,420 --> 00:26:29,963
Mari kita tengok.

257
00:27:06,124 --> 00:27:11,880
DISEMBER

258
00:27:19,554 --> 00:27:21,431
FAKULTI KEJURUTERAAN MEKANIKAL

259
00:27:21,514 --> 00:27:23,016
PERMOHONAN TELAH DIHANTAR

260
00:27:23,099 --> 00:27:24,309
Dah siap.

261
00:27:24,392 --> 00:27:26,561
Mujurlah dapat hantar awal.

262
00:27:27,395 --> 00:27:30,148
Keputusan akan keluar
pada 4 Februari, jadi…

263
00:27:30,231 --> 00:27:31,983
Awak tenang saja.

264
00:27:42,994 --> 00:27:44,788
Ya, cantik.

265
00:28:03,640 --> 00:28:05,058
Eun-a.

266
00:28:09,979 --> 00:28:11,981
Selamat Krismas awal.

267
00:28:25,620 --> 00:28:26,621
Tetamu dah sampai.

268
00:28:26,704 --> 00:28:28,373
Dah siap.

269
00:28:30,041 --> 00:28:32,794
Sebab awak, saya dapat
pasukan khidmat tetamu.

270
00:28:32,877 --> 00:28:33,753
Terima kasih.

271
00:28:34,754 --> 00:28:37,507
Dengar kata awak minta
nak bekerja dengan saya.

272
00:28:38,550 --> 00:28:40,176
Sebab awak bagus.

273
00:28:43,304 --> 00:28:46,808
Saya rasa Seon-gyu terganggu
sebab dia kena layan

274
00:28:46,891 --> 00:28:48,560
orang lain-lain setiap kali.

275
00:28:48,643 --> 00:28:50,645
Dia nampak bergelut.

276
00:28:51,229 --> 00:28:52,856
Jadi, adillah.

277
00:28:55,358 --> 00:28:57,110
Awak belum makan malam, bukan?

278
00:28:57,193 --> 00:29:00,655
Makan ini satu,
hantar satu lagi kepada Eun-a.

279
00:29:02,532 --> 00:29:05,869
Kalau ada tetamu,
dia tak pernah keluar bilik.

280
00:29:11,332 --> 00:29:13,209
Apa perasaan awak lepas hantar?

281
00:29:13,293 --> 00:29:16,796
Cikgu yang hantar.
Dia yang tekan butang "hantar".

282
00:29:16,880 --> 00:29:18,047
Dia tekankan?

283
00:29:18,715 --> 00:29:20,508
Saya tak suruh pun,

284
00:29:20,592 --> 00:29:22,302
tapi lebih mudah dia yang tekan.

285
00:29:23,970 --> 00:29:25,930
Mesti gementar tekan sendiri.

286
00:29:28,558 --> 00:29:31,352
Orang dewasa selalu kena hadap
benda menyerabutkan begini?

287
00:29:32,103 --> 00:29:35,023
Kenapa saya selalu gementar dan takut?

288
00:30:09,015 --> 00:30:10,683
PERMOHONAN

289
00:30:18,817 --> 00:30:21,402
Kalau dah, cikgu tekan sekarang.
Cikgu hantar sekarang.

290
00:30:21,486 --> 00:30:23,279
Cikgu, sekejap.

291
00:30:23,363 --> 00:30:26,241
- Awak dah buat yang terbaik.
- Sekejap.

292
00:30:26,324 --> 00:30:28,493
- Cikgu tak boleh tunggu.
- Tunggu dulu!

293
00:30:28,576 --> 00:30:30,161
Hari ini hari Krismas.

294
00:30:30,245 --> 00:30:31,746
Boleh saya berdoa dulu?

295
00:30:35,708 --> 00:30:36,960
Saya kena berdiri.

296
00:30:37,961 --> 00:30:39,045
Tak apa. Berdoa dulu.

297
00:30:39,128 --> 00:30:41,506
- Saya tak sedap hati,
- Berdoalah.

298
00:30:45,301 --> 00:30:47,262
Harapnya boleh balik hari ini.

299
00:30:49,764 --> 00:30:51,599
Santa, saya nak masuk universiti.

300
00:30:51,683 --> 00:30:54,686
JANUARI

301
00:31:10,493 --> 00:31:11,953
Terkejut saya!

302
00:31:13,037 --> 00:31:14,372
Kenapa menyorok di situ?

303
00:31:14,956 --> 00:31:15,957
Gelaplah.

304
00:31:16,916 --> 00:31:18,585
- Bukalah lampu.
- Tak apa…

305
00:31:20,253 --> 00:31:21,462
Saya okey.

306
00:31:27,510 --> 00:31:28,636
Marilah.

307
00:31:54,162 --> 00:31:56,915
Satu benda yang pasti,
rumah ini banyak makanan.

308
00:31:58,333 --> 00:31:59,500
Makan sedap-sedap.

309
00:32:01,669 --> 00:32:03,796
Kami perlukan wain yang awak ambil itu,

310
00:32:05,340 --> 00:32:06,591
ambil yang ada di sini.

311
00:32:08,509 --> 00:32:09,510
Okey.

312
00:32:42,460 --> 00:32:43,920
Selamat Tahun Baru.

313
00:33:29,340 --> 00:33:31,509
Hari pertama 20 tahun
bersama Yeon Tae-seo.

314
00:33:37,181 --> 00:33:38,224
Tak ada gelas.

315
00:33:58,411 --> 00:33:59,245
Manis.

316
00:34:13,843 --> 00:34:14,969
Sedap juga.

317
00:34:18,639 --> 00:34:19,640
Ini bukan arak.

318
00:34:19,724 --> 00:34:21,100
Araklah.

319
00:34:55,843 --> 00:34:57,095
Jom.

320
00:35:29,669 --> 00:35:30,920
Eun-a!

321
00:35:32,922 --> 00:35:33,923
Diamlah.

322
00:35:42,014 --> 00:35:47,478
FEBRUARI

323
00:35:48,980 --> 00:35:51,691
Okey, nak ucap selamat?

324
00:35:53,317 --> 00:35:54,902
Tahniah.

325
00:35:55,862 --> 00:35:59,740
Budak kampung kecil masuk
Universiti Kebangsaan Hanguk. Tahniah.

326
00:35:59,824 --> 00:36:01,868
Apa pula cakap begitu.

327
00:36:01,951 --> 00:36:04,078
Semuanya sebab cikgu ini.

328
00:36:04,162 --> 00:36:06,414
Saya tak buat apa-apa pun.

329
00:36:06,497 --> 00:36:08,166
Dia yang rajin belajar.

330
00:36:08,249 --> 00:36:10,585
Anak En. Mo tak dapat?

331
00:36:10,668 --> 00:36:12,044
Dia belum tahu lagi.

332
00:36:12,128 --> 00:36:13,963
Ini baru pusingan pertama,

333
00:36:14,046 --> 00:36:16,549
nanti ada kedua dan ketiga.

334
00:36:16,632 --> 00:36:18,259
Keputusan keluar berperingkat.

335
00:36:18,342 --> 00:36:20,386
Jadi, agak rumitlah.

336
00:36:20,469 --> 00:36:22,471
Aduhai, susah-susah saja.

337
00:36:22,555 --> 00:36:24,265
Makanlah, cikgu.

338
00:36:24,348 --> 00:36:25,600
- Tahniah.
- Syabas.

339
00:36:25,683 --> 00:36:27,059
Terima kasih.

340
00:36:27,143 --> 00:36:28,936
Cikgu,

341
00:36:29,020 --> 00:36:31,355
jelaskan biar saya faham.

342
00:36:31,439 --> 00:36:34,400
Ada tempoh kemasukan tambahan,

343
00:36:34,483 --> 00:36:38,988
keputusan belum habis keluar
sampai hujung Februari.

344
00:36:39,071 --> 00:36:40,948
Apa maksudnya?

345
00:36:41,032 --> 00:36:43,784
Mesti Eun-a resah menunggu keputusan.

346
00:36:45,161 --> 00:36:46,037
Itulah.

347
00:36:52,501 --> 00:36:53,628
Ini kali pertama.

348
00:36:54,545 --> 00:36:55,546
Naik Kereta Api Laut?

349
00:36:56,714 --> 00:36:57,798
INI KERETA API LAUT

350
00:36:57,882 --> 00:37:01,385
Hanya beroperasi pada siang hari
dan melalui jalan pantai.

351
00:37:01,469 --> 00:37:04,472
Dari Gangneung ke Samcheok
mengambil masa sejam 40 minit,

352
00:37:04,555 --> 00:37:06,140
jadi kalau kita ke sana…

353
00:37:06,224 --> 00:37:08,893
Kita boleh bersama tiga jam setengah.

354
00:37:09,644 --> 00:37:10,645
Ya.

355
00:37:14,357 --> 00:37:15,733
Waktu saya kecil,

356
00:37:16,692 --> 00:37:18,778
mak saya pernah bekerja di sini sekejap.

357
00:37:20,029 --> 00:37:22,281
Saya berangan nak jadi
pemandu Kereta Api Laut.

358
00:37:23,491 --> 00:37:25,284
Mungkin sebab nampak hebat.

359
00:37:28,496 --> 00:37:29,830
Bagusnya.

360
00:37:32,375 --> 00:37:34,418
Awak nak cakap apa sampai kita ke sini?

361
00:37:41,592 --> 00:37:43,803
Saya dah nak pergi ke Seoul.

362
00:37:45,471 --> 00:37:48,641
Masa tinggal di Seoul dulu,
saya ada kawan nama Hyeong-seok.

363
00:37:48,724 --> 00:37:50,393
Ayah dia ada pusat belajar.

364
00:37:51,644 --> 00:37:54,647
Dia beri saya guna percuma
dan banyak tolong saya.

365
00:37:56,023 --> 00:37:58,401
Dia minta saya buat tutor
bermula Februari.

366
00:37:59,318 --> 00:38:00,820
Saya asyik tolak,

367
00:38:01,904 --> 00:38:04,240
tapi saya rasa saya dah kena pergi.

368
00:38:08,744 --> 00:38:09,912
Begitu.

369
00:38:11,998 --> 00:38:12,832
Awak patut pergi.

370
00:38:14,292 --> 00:38:15,543
Majlis kemasukan?

371
00:38:15,626 --> 00:38:17,086
Hui-seo pergi nanti?

372
00:38:17,670 --> 00:38:19,046
Dia tak boleh pergi.

373
00:38:19,130 --> 00:38:20,840
Belum boleh tempuh perjalanan jauh.

374
00:38:21,382 --> 00:38:22,591
Mesti Hui-seo sedih.

375
00:38:24,176 --> 00:38:25,303
Ada tempat tinggal?

376
00:38:25,386 --> 00:38:27,930
Ya, pejabat pusat belajar itu ada katil.

377
00:38:28,014 --> 00:38:30,057
Takkan nak tidur di pejabat?

378
00:38:32,268 --> 00:38:33,352
Pilunya hati.

379
00:38:35,104 --> 00:38:36,355
Tak ada apa-apalah.

380
00:38:38,024 --> 00:38:39,942
Mesti lagi pilu tunggu keputusan awak.

381
00:38:42,695 --> 00:38:43,571
Saya?

382
00:38:44,238 --> 00:38:46,324
Satu daripada tiga pilihan saya

383
00:38:46,907 --> 00:38:48,701
dekat dengan awak,

384
00:38:49,410 --> 00:38:51,454
tapi kebarangkaliannya rendah.

385
00:38:51,537 --> 00:38:54,206
Satu lagi antara sini dan Seoul,
tapi tak pasti.

386
00:38:54,290 --> 00:38:56,542
Satu lagi di Gangneung.

387
00:38:57,960 --> 00:39:01,047
Cikgu cakap universiti itu bagus,
program yang ada pun bagus.

388
00:39:02,256 --> 00:39:03,132
Tapi…

389
00:39:04,342 --> 00:39:06,052
Jauh daripada awak.

390
00:39:06,677 --> 00:39:10,848
Kena tunggu lebih sebulan
buat saya resah dan tak yakin.

391
00:39:11,474 --> 00:39:13,309
Sebab berlarutan lama sangat,

392
00:39:13,392 --> 00:39:15,353
tak sangka Februari dah nak berlalu.

393
00:39:15,895 --> 00:39:17,104
Rasa macam lama sangat.

394
00:39:26,530 --> 00:39:28,032
Pasti akan berlalu.

395
00:39:30,242 --> 00:39:31,952
Harapnya begitulah.

396
00:39:40,336 --> 00:39:42,505
Pengakhiran yang memang terasa.

397
00:39:43,631 --> 00:39:45,716
Saya harap pengakhirannya baik.

398
00:40:11,992 --> 00:40:12,952
Sekejap.

399
00:40:17,289 --> 00:40:19,417
Tak banyak pun, tapi ambillah.

400
00:40:19,500 --> 00:40:21,001
Tak apa. Saya ada duit.

401
00:40:21,085 --> 00:40:22,795
Belilah baju.

402
00:40:24,463 --> 00:40:26,132
Nenek kamu rasa bersalah

403
00:40:26,215 --> 00:40:28,884
kami tak beli kamu pakaian

404
00:40:28,968 --> 00:40:31,053
untuk majlis kemasukan nanti.

405
00:40:32,304 --> 00:40:34,390
Kami tak mampu belikan sut,

406
00:40:34,473 --> 00:40:37,893
tapi setidaknya kamu belilah kot.

407
00:40:37,977 --> 00:40:39,728
Yang nampak rasmi.

408
00:40:40,479 --> 00:40:42,857
Kamu kena selalu
pakai lawa-lawa di bandar.

409
00:40:42,940 --> 00:40:45,067
Nah. Beli sepasang.

410
00:40:46,360 --> 00:40:47,528
Terima kasih.

411
00:40:49,822 --> 00:40:53,075
Daripada biasiswa ke tutor,
semua kamu buat sendiri.

412
00:40:53,159 --> 00:40:54,660
Kami rasa bersalah.

413
00:40:58,080 --> 00:40:58,998
Nanti saya balik.

414
00:41:00,332 --> 00:41:03,210
Tak payah. Kamu belajar sajalah.
Membazir duit saja.

415
00:41:04,587 --> 00:41:06,255
Pastikan kamu telefon Hui-seo saja.

416
00:41:09,341 --> 00:41:12,761
Datuk ingatkan dia akan marah
tak dapat pergi majlis kamu,

417
00:41:12,845 --> 00:41:13,888
tapi dia diam saja.

418
00:41:18,684 --> 00:41:22,521
Setidaknya hari majlis itu
tak sama dengan hari memperingati.

419
00:41:23,731 --> 00:41:25,107
Ini tahun pertama.

420
00:41:32,531 --> 00:41:34,325
Saya akan pergi ziarah.

421
00:41:35,284 --> 00:41:36,619
Datuk duduk dengan Hui-seo.

422
00:41:41,790 --> 00:41:42,750
Yalah.

423
00:41:43,667 --> 00:41:44,960
Kamu pergilah.

424
00:41:45,878 --> 00:41:46,712
Okey.

425
00:41:53,385 --> 00:41:59,183
RUANG MENUNGGU (TIKET)

426
00:42:02,436 --> 00:42:05,898
<i>Awak naik bas ekspres ke Seoul?</i>

427
00:42:06,690 --> 00:42:07,525
Eun-a.

428
00:42:09,527 --> 00:42:11,487
STESEN CHEONGGYEONG

429
00:42:11,570 --> 00:42:13,322
Saya tunggu awak di sini.

430
00:42:13,405 --> 00:42:15,407
Saya ingatkan awak naik kereta api.

431
00:42:15,491 --> 00:42:16,450
Saya memang cuai.

432
00:42:18,160 --> 00:42:19,370
Saya…

433
00:42:19,453 --> 00:42:22,456
Saya tahu awak larang,
tapi saya rasa bersalah tak hantar awak.

434
00:42:22,540 --> 00:42:25,709
Biar saya hantar. Saya beli dua tiket,
kita boleh terus pergi.

435
00:42:25,793 --> 00:42:26,919
Jangan merepek.

436
00:42:40,558 --> 00:42:42,810
Takkan saya nak biar awak balik
seorang diri?

437
00:42:43,686 --> 00:42:44,853
Hari ini saja.

438
00:42:51,402 --> 00:42:52,820
Tak apalah.

439
00:42:56,115 --> 00:42:57,533
Turun di hentian seterusnya.

440
00:42:58,534 --> 00:43:01,620
Saya tak boleh tengok awak balik sendiri.
Saya hantar awak…

441
00:43:01,704 --> 00:43:03,247
Awak boleh seorang, saya tak?

442
00:43:04,915 --> 00:43:06,750
Merepek. Tak apalah.

443
00:43:09,962 --> 00:43:11,630
Dah lebih sejam.

444
00:43:11,714 --> 00:43:13,132
Kita tak ada masa.

445
00:43:13,215 --> 00:43:14,967
Sampai bila awak nak begini?

446
00:43:25,769 --> 00:43:28,063
LOG MASUK

447
00:43:31,108 --> 00:43:33,277
SENARAI LAGU

448
00:43:35,738 --> 00:43:36,655
Ini akaun saya.

449
00:43:37,573 --> 00:43:41,577
Kalau saya guna, akan keluar,
"Sedang distrim."

450
00:43:42,328 --> 00:43:44,747
Boleh guna sama-sama.
Kita akan dengar serentak.

451
00:43:45,414 --> 00:43:46,415
Dengan cara itu,

452
00:43:47,458 --> 00:43:49,710
kita akan rasa macam kita bersama.

453
00:43:51,837 --> 00:43:53,714
Akan rasa macam kita bersama.

454
00:43:53,797 --> 00:43:54,882
Rasa macam kita bersama

455
00:43:56,467 --> 00:43:58,093
dianggap macam bersama.

456
00:44:01,555 --> 00:44:02,890
Saya suka.

457
00:44:02,973 --> 00:44:04,433
Apa lagi benda lain

458
00:44:04,516 --> 00:44:06,101
yang buat kita rasa bersama?

459
00:44:07,811 --> 00:44:10,481
Kongsi gambar yang kita ambil?
Mari kita ambil satu.

460
00:44:14,068 --> 00:44:14,902
Senyum.

461
00:44:21,450 --> 00:44:22,743
STESEN CHEONGYANGNI

462
00:44:22,826 --> 00:44:25,162
Pak cik, berapa lama kena tunggu?

463
00:44:25,245 --> 00:44:26,163
Sejam.

464
00:44:26,246 --> 00:44:27,081
Apa?

465
00:44:30,959 --> 00:44:33,545
Pergilah. Kita berpisah di sini.
Ini kelas pertama awak.

466
00:44:34,463 --> 00:44:35,422
Eun-a.

467
00:44:38,384 --> 00:44:40,135
Ini lebih susah

468
00:44:40,719 --> 00:44:42,096
daripada yang saya sangka.

469
00:44:43,180 --> 00:44:44,431
Saya tak bolehlah.

470
00:44:45,307 --> 00:44:46,392
Saya boleh.

471
00:44:46,475 --> 00:44:49,436
Tak, macam mana
saya nak biar awak balik seorang?

472
00:44:50,896 --> 00:44:53,107
Biar macam ini sajalah.

473
00:44:53,190 --> 00:44:56,735
Saya mungkin dapat
universiti dekat atau tak.

474
00:44:57,444 --> 00:44:58,987
Saya tak tahu apa akan jadi.

475
00:45:00,781 --> 00:45:02,032
Hidup saya tak pasti.

476
00:45:03,784 --> 00:45:05,661
Apa pun, kita kena terus begini,

477
00:45:05,744 --> 00:45:08,247
tapi kalau awak rasa bersalah,
susah kita nak jumpa.

478
00:45:12,793 --> 00:45:13,794
Nak gila rasanya.

479
00:45:16,964 --> 00:45:18,048
Saya…

480
00:45:18,715 --> 00:45:20,050
Saya akan buat yang terbaik.

481
00:45:20,884 --> 00:45:21,802
Okey.

482
00:45:28,767 --> 00:45:29,643
Oh, Tuhan.

483
00:45:30,769 --> 00:45:31,770
Kenapa?

484
00:45:31,854 --> 00:45:33,355
Apa dia?

485
00:45:33,439 --> 00:45:34,481
Saya dapat.

486
00:45:35,107 --> 00:45:35,941
Apa?

487
00:45:36,525 --> 00:45:38,235
UNIVERSITI GANGNEUNG WONKYEONG

488
00:45:39,445 --> 00:45:41,113
Tak mungkin! Saya dapat!

489
00:45:41,196 --> 00:45:43,615
Nampak? Saya dapat sebab saya dengan awak!

490
00:45:44,825 --> 00:45:47,077
Oh, Tuhan. Tapi jauh sikit daripada awak.

491
00:45:47,161 --> 00:45:49,455
Itu tak penting sekarang!

492
00:45:50,622 --> 00:45:52,416
Tahniah!

493
00:45:54,168 --> 00:45:57,588
- Awak layak dapat.
- Oh, Tuhan. Gembiranya.

494
00:45:57,671 --> 00:46:01,717
MAC

495
00:46:47,596 --> 00:46:49,389
- Cantik.
- Kemas dan bersih.

496
00:46:49,473 --> 00:46:50,807
Rakan sebilik, ya?

497
00:46:50,891 --> 00:46:52,434
Harap kamu berdua berbaik.

498
00:46:53,143 --> 00:46:56,271
- Lembutnya tilam.
- Sayang, jangan duduk di situ.

499
00:46:56,355 --> 00:46:58,357
Kenapa pula? Marilah duduk, mak.

500
00:47:01,902 --> 00:47:02,986
Elok.

501
00:47:15,749 --> 00:47:16,833
Hui-seo…

502
00:47:19,169 --> 00:47:21,338
Saya akan bawa apabila dia besar nanti.

503
00:47:29,137 --> 00:47:30,931
Jangan risau tentang dia.

504
00:47:34,643 --> 00:47:37,104
Jangan risau tentang datuk dan nenek.

505
00:47:41,984 --> 00:47:43,777
Saya akan jaga semua orang.

506
00:47:50,659 --> 00:47:51,660
Oh, ya.

507
00:47:53,912 --> 00:47:56,290
Saya dapat masuk universiti yang mak nak.

508
00:48:03,630 --> 00:48:05,716
Mesti mak suka kalau dapat tengok.

509
00:48:13,724 --> 00:48:14,725
Mak.

510
00:48:17,394 --> 00:48:18,270
Ayah.

511
00:48:58,977 --> 00:49:00,771
Boleh saya duduk di sini?

512
00:49:00,854 --> 00:49:01,813
Boleh.

513
00:49:12,532 --> 00:49:13,659
Saya Park Na-ri.

514
00:49:15,285 --> 00:49:16,203
Saya Mo Eun-a.

515
00:49:18,205 --> 00:49:21,333
Hei, nombor pelajar awak
lepas nombor saya.

516
00:49:21,416 --> 00:49:22,417
Kebetulan pula.

517
00:49:24,670 --> 00:49:26,672
Saya dari Seoul. Awak?

518
00:49:26,755 --> 00:49:28,965
Saya berdekatan. Naik bas 20 minit.

519
00:49:29,049 --> 00:49:30,217
- Dua puluh minit?
- Ya.

520
00:49:36,431 --> 00:49:38,100
Biar betul? Kelas elektif pun sama?

521
00:49:38,183 --> 00:49:40,352
Biar betul? Mari duduk di sini.

522
00:49:47,818 --> 00:49:48,735
Apa itu?

523
00:49:52,823 --> 00:49:55,409
- Nak pilih satu?
- Comelnya.

524
00:49:56,618 --> 00:49:57,869
- Yang ini.
- Boleh.

525
00:49:57,953 --> 00:49:59,663
- Nah.
- Terima kasih.

526
00:50:00,914 --> 00:50:05,585
Kelas ini bernama
Reka Bentuk Kejuruteraan Kreatif.

527
00:50:05,669 --> 00:50:07,295
Di sini, kamu akan menilai

528
00:50:07,379 --> 00:50:10,882
apa yang melangkaui mesin.

529
00:50:10,966 --> 00:50:12,926
Mesin hebat terhasil apabila kamu faham

530
00:50:13,009 --> 00:50:14,261
fungsi dan nilainya.

531
00:50:14,344 --> 00:50:17,973
Untuk kelas ini,
kamu perlukan keupayaan matematik

532
00:50:18,056 --> 00:50:19,808
dan akal yang mampu berfikir.

533
00:50:19,891 --> 00:50:22,853
Selebihnya kamu akan belajar
dalam kelas hari ini.

534
00:50:24,062 --> 00:50:26,314
Memang nak belajar
pendidikan awal kanak-kanak?

535
00:50:26,398 --> 00:50:28,692
Ya, sebab saya suka budak-budak.

536
00:50:30,193 --> 00:50:33,655
Tapi saya tak minat mengajar.
Saya harap jurusan lain.

537
00:50:35,532 --> 00:50:38,493
Saya pilih di sini sebab jurusan,
tapi sekarang saya tak yakin.

538
00:50:41,496 --> 00:50:43,540
Tapi seronok dapat tengok pantai.

539
00:50:44,875 --> 00:50:46,752
Berbaloi ponteng kelas.

540
00:50:46,835 --> 00:50:47,669
Itulah.

541
00:50:49,755 --> 00:50:51,798
Kopi mesin layan diri di sini sedap.

542
00:50:51,882 --> 00:50:54,259
PASAR SORI

543
00:50:54,342 --> 00:50:55,385
- Nak cuba?
- Jom.

544
00:50:58,388 --> 00:50:59,765
<i>Kami terus rapat.</i>

545
00:50:59,848 --> 00:51:01,391
<i>Saya teroka Gangneung sebab dia.</i>

546
00:51:01,475 --> 00:51:03,477
Nanti awak datang, saya bawa awak.

547
00:51:03,560 --> 00:51:04,895
Okey.

548
00:51:07,314 --> 00:51:09,524
<i>Saya ada pelekat sama dengan Na-ri,</i>

549
00:51:09,608 --> 00:51:11,735
<i>tapi tak ada apa-apa yang sama</i>
<i>dengan awak.</i>

550
00:51:14,613 --> 00:51:15,781
Awak nak buat apa?

551
00:51:17,657 --> 00:51:19,409
Saya ada idea menarik.

552
00:51:19,493 --> 00:51:21,912
Apa kata saya buat pelekat
guna lukisan saya?

553
00:51:21,995 --> 00:51:24,206
<i>Pelekat sayur sama untuk kelas berbeza.</i>

554
00:51:24,790 --> 00:51:25,832
<i>Beritahu nama kelas.</i>

555
00:51:25,916 --> 00:51:27,584
Nanti saya lukis untuk setiap satu.

556
00:51:27,667 --> 00:51:28,585
Saya pandai lukis.

557
00:51:30,337 --> 00:51:32,214
Matematik Kejuruteraan.

558
00:51:32,297 --> 00:51:33,131
<i>Kacang merah.</i>

559
00:51:33,215 --> 00:51:34,800
Sangat susah nak tanggalkan.

560
00:51:36,551 --> 00:51:39,763
Susah nak tanggalkan? Kalau begitu…

561
00:51:39,846 --> 00:51:40,972
APRIL

562
00:51:43,600 --> 00:51:45,185
- Kim Na-rae.
- Saya.

563
00:51:47,062 --> 00:51:48,230
Kim Ji-ho.

564
00:51:49,731 --> 00:51:50,690
Ji-ho?

565
00:51:52,234 --> 00:51:53,985
- Mo Eun-a.
- Saya.

566
00:51:55,612 --> 00:51:56,613
Park Na-ri.

567
00:51:57,739 --> 00:51:59,324
Oh, ya. Na-ri cuti.

568
00:52:00,492 --> 00:52:04,079
Baru sebulan kelas, dah ada yang cuti.

569
00:52:06,122 --> 00:52:08,208
- Park Seo-yeon.
- Saya.

570
00:52:08,291 --> 00:52:10,293
- Song A-yeong.
- Saya.

571
00:52:21,304 --> 00:52:22,472
SENARAI LAGU

572
00:52:31,523 --> 00:52:33,525
TAE-SEO

573
00:52:33,608 --> 00:52:35,652
<i>Bunga di Seoul dah mekar?</i>

574
00:52:35,735 --> 00:52:37,237
<i>Di sini sangat mekar.</i>

575
00:52:37,320 --> 00:52:39,447
<i>Hantar gambar bunga di universiti awak.</i>

576
00:52:39,531 --> 00:52:43,118
<i>Gambar awak depan bunga sekali.</i>

577
00:52:47,289 --> 00:52:49,624
<i>Saya rindu awak, Tae-seo.</i>

578
00:52:50,792 --> 00:52:52,836
- Helo.
- Helo.

579
00:53:05,765 --> 00:53:08,393
<i>Lepas tutor nanti saya ke universiti,</i>
<i>nanti saya hantar.</i>

580
00:53:13,481 --> 00:53:16,026
EKSPRES HONGDONG

581
00:53:23,158 --> 00:53:26,494
Kelas tutor dia biasanya dua jam, jadi…

582
00:53:28,413 --> 00:53:30,624
<i>Lepas kelas tutor, telefon saya, okey?</i>

583
00:53:49,309 --> 00:53:50,894
<i>Tutor habis pukul berapa?</i>

584
00:53:51,770 --> 00:53:53,563
TUTOR HABIS PUKUL BERAPA?

585
00:54:01,988 --> 00:54:03,823
<i>Hari ini saya ada dua sesi,</i>

586
00:54:03,907 --> 00:54:05,617
<i>lepas itu saya terus ke universiti,</i>

587
00:54:05,700 --> 00:54:06,910
<i>jadi sekitar 10.00 malam.</i>

588
00:54:10,830 --> 00:54:13,750
TERMINAL BAS DONGSEOUL
TIKET

589
00:54:16,711 --> 00:54:19,089
Satu tiket ke Gangneung.

590
00:54:19,172 --> 00:54:20,298
Gangneung?

591
00:54:21,007 --> 00:54:22,217
Tambangnya 10,600 won.

592
00:54:26,805 --> 00:54:27,639
Ayah.

593
00:54:29,766 --> 00:54:31,059
Kenapa minta ayah ambil?

594
00:54:31,810 --> 00:54:32,852
Tak nak sendirian.

595
00:54:33,853 --> 00:54:35,814
Kita keluar jalan-jalan malam?

596
00:54:35,897 --> 00:54:38,024
Nak pergi mana? Jom makan sasyimi.

597
00:54:39,985 --> 00:54:41,027
Saya penat.

598
00:54:55,709 --> 00:54:57,502
Kita nak makan apa?

599
00:54:57,585 --> 00:54:59,587
Ada teringin apa-apa?

600
00:55:00,505 --> 00:55:01,881
Saya tak kisah.

601
00:55:03,133 --> 00:55:04,175
Nak tanya Eun-a?

602
00:55:04,259 --> 00:55:06,386
Eun-a, ada nak makan apa-apa?

603
00:55:07,595 --> 00:55:08,763
Eun-a, awak tidur?

604
00:55:10,598 --> 00:55:12,017
Mesti dia betul-betul penat.

605
00:55:12,100 --> 00:55:14,394
Biarlah dia tidur.

606
00:55:15,103 --> 00:55:16,855
Dah lama kita tak keluar bertiga.

607
00:55:17,480 --> 00:55:19,441
Mesti seronok kalau dapat berbual.

608
00:55:19,524 --> 00:55:21,151
<i>Tak sedar pun dah semekar ini.</i>

609
00:55:22,610 --> 00:55:23,611
<i>Nak saya telefon?</i>

610
00:55:24,195 --> 00:55:25,321
<i>Ada apa-apa berlaku?</i>

611
00:55:26,656 --> 00:55:29,200
<i>Saya cuma teringatkan awak.</i>

612
00:55:30,785 --> 00:55:33,788
<i>Saya boleh bergerak pagi</i>
<i>hujung minggu ini.</i>

613
00:55:33,872 --> 00:55:34,831
<i>Kita jumpa awal.</i>

614
00:55:35,790 --> 00:55:37,208
<i>Saya nak pergi ke Seoul.</i>

615
00:55:38,168 --> 00:55:39,461
<i>Ini giliran saya.</i>

616
00:55:39,544 --> 00:55:40,795
<i>Saya ke tempat awak.</i>

617
00:55:40,879 --> 00:55:42,380
<i>Tak, saya ke tempat awak.</i>

618
00:55:42,922 --> 00:55:44,340
<i>Awak guna masa awak.</i>

619
00:55:44,424 --> 00:55:45,759
<i>Jangan bazirkan.</i>

620
00:55:45,842 --> 00:55:47,469
Helo, Hyeong-seok? Ya.

621
00:55:48,136 --> 00:55:49,929
<i>Masa awak pun berharga.</i>

622
00:55:50,013 --> 00:55:50,972
<i>Biar saya pergi.</i>

623
00:55:55,643 --> 00:55:57,896
<i>Masa saya berlalu begitu saja,</i>

624
00:55:58,772 --> 00:56:02,108
<i>tapi masa awak perlu digunakan</i>
<i>untuk mencapai impian.</i>

625
00:56:02,192 --> 00:56:03,318
<i>Lain.</i>

626
00:56:05,612 --> 00:56:07,280
<i>Jangan hantar gambar gelap lagi.</i>

627
00:56:08,323 --> 00:56:10,075
<i>Saya rindu awak, Tae-seo.</i>

628
00:56:11,242 --> 00:56:12,285
<i>Sangat rindu.</i>

629
00:57:08,007 --> 00:57:08,967
Seronoknya.

630
00:57:09,050 --> 00:57:10,260
Awak rindu saya?

631
00:57:12,262 --> 00:57:13,096
Mestilah.

632
00:57:16,391 --> 00:57:23,356
MEI

633
00:57:39,205 --> 00:57:41,583
Setiap kali pegang rokok, awak muncul.

634
00:57:41,666 --> 00:57:42,709
Menakutkan.

635
00:57:46,796 --> 00:57:48,590
Seronok bekerja di hotel, bukan?

636
00:57:49,340 --> 00:57:51,384
Saya seronok setiap kali
nampak staf hotel.

637
00:57:51,468 --> 00:57:52,844
Cubalah.

638
00:57:53,344 --> 00:57:55,638
Ramai orang muda kerja sambilan di hotel.

639
00:57:55,722 --> 00:57:56,973
Awak cuti belajar?

640
00:57:58,349 --> 00:57:59,809
Kenapa pula cuti?

641
00:57:59,893 --> 00:58:01,686
Saya takkan buat apa-apa membuta tuli

642
00:58:01,769 --> 00:58:03,688
sebab semua orang buat.

643
00:58:04,814 --> 00:58:05,773
Menyampah betul.

644
00:58:07,609 --> 00:58:09,861
Saya tahu awak pelajar universiti,

645
00:58:09,944 --> 00:58:12,322
sekarang bukan cuti,
kenapa tak pergi kelas?

646
00:58:12,405 --> 00:58:15,325
Seharian awak di sini,
dari kelmarin naik basikal.

647
00:58:16,075 --> 00:58:17,202
Orang pertama tanya.

648
00:58:17,785 --> 00:58:19,787
Seminggu saya ponteng dan bermalasan,

649
00:58:19,871 --> 00:58:20,955
tak ada yang tanya.

650
00:58:21,039 --> 00:58:22,832
Universiti pun tak cari.

651
00:58:22,916 --> 00:58:25,126
Ayah pun tak tanya kenapa.

652
00:58:25,960 --> 00:58:27,462
Mungkin tak ada yang peduli.

653
00:58:28,046 --> 00:58:29,631
Terima kasih sebab tanya.

654
00:58:30,173 --> 00:58:32,675
Saya tak pergi sebab tak rasa nak pergi.

655
00:58:32,759 --> 00:58:34,677
Kalau nak buat separuh hati,

656
00:58:34,761 --> 00:58:37,180
lebih baik cuti belajar, buat benda lain.

657
00:58:37,263 --> 00:58:38,640
Awak kata nak berdikari.

658
00:58:39,265 --> 00:58:40,808
Dalam keadaan sekarang,

659
00:58:40,892 --> 00:58:43,144
ayah awak takkan perasan
awak tak pergi kelas.

660
00:58:43,228 --> 00:58:45,355
Kalau saya jadi awak, saya pindah.

661
00:58:49,359 --> 00:58:51,694
Tiba-tiba saja. Keadaan apa?

662
00:58:51,778 --> 00:58:53,696
Pergilah jemput tetamu.

663
00:58:53,780 --> 00:58:56,866
Tempahan tengah hari,
tapi sekarang dah jam berapa?

664
00:58:58,034 --> 00:59:00,537
So-hyeon buat pengumuman tergempar.

665
00:59:00,620 --> 00:59:02,622
Tak boleh rosakkan suasana.

666
00:59:03,289 --> 00:59:04,582
Pengumuman?

667
00:59:05,583 --> 00:59:08,294
- Kamu berdua serasi.
- Saya tumpang gembira.

668
00:59:08,378 --> 00:59:09,671
Tahniah.

669
00:59:09,754 --> 00:59:11,130
- Tahniah.
- Tahniah.

670
00:59:11,214 --> 00:59:12,131
Tahniah.

671
00:59:12,215 --> 00:59:14,133
- Saya bawa wain lagi.
- Baiklah.

672
00:59:16,970 --> 00:59:18,054
Minum.

673
00:59:25,103 --> 00:59:26,396
Tepat pada masanya.

674
00:59:26,479 --> 00:59:28,314
Ayah awak baru umumkan perkahwinan.

675
00:59:28,398 --> 00:59:29,649
Ucaplah tahniah.

676
00:59:53,214 --> 00:59:54,424
Lelaki Unit 610 itu?

677
00:59:55,633 --> 00:59:56,884
Sekarang baru tanya.

678
00:59:58,011 --> 00:59:59,262
Saya akan putuskan.

679
00:59:59,345 --> 01:00:00,763
Baru nak putuskan?

680
01:00:01,931 --> 01:00:03,808
Seon-gyu tahu semuanya.

681
01:00:04,726 --> 01:00:07,103
Dia kata dia akan beritahu lepas fikir,

682
01:00:07,186 --> 01:00:08,896
jadi saya tak sempat putus.

683
01:00:11,065 --> 01:00:11,899
Eun-a.

684
01:00:11,983 --> 01:00:16,654
Cinta tak ada susunan yang betul.

685
01:00:16,738 --> 01:00:18,906
Patutlah awak sentiasa ada jantan.

686
01:00:18,990 --> 01:00:20,325
Tak pernah sendiri.

687
01:00:20,408 --> 01:00:22,368
- Jaga mulut.
- Awaklah jaga.

688
01:00:22,452 --> 01:00:23,953
Berani main kayu tiga?

689
01:00:28,333 --> 01:00:30,001
Orang saya suka ialah Seon-gyu.

690
01:00:30,084 --> 01:00:31,628
Lelaki Unit 610 pun tahu.

691
01:00:31,711 --> 01:00:34,339
Saya tak pernah perdaya sesiapa.

692
01:00:34,422 --> 01:00:36,716
Jadi, awak akan buat sesuka hati,

693
01:00:36,799 --> 01:00:38,718
orang sekeliling kena terima?

694
01:00:39,927 --> 01:00:42,055
Ayah saya terima kegilaan ini?

695
01:00:44,682 --> 01:00:46,184
Awak fikir ayah saya apa?

696
01:00:47,226 --> 01:00:49,812
Dia sangat baik, tapi orang macam awak…

697
01:00:49,896 --> 01:00:50,813
Sampai hari ini.

698
01:00:50,897 --> 01:00:52,815
Saya terima cacian awak hari ini,

699
01:00:52,899 --> 01:00:54,150
tapi selepas ini,

700
01:00:54,942 --> 01:00:56,110
tak lagi.

701
01:01:01,449 --> 01:01:02,283
Mo Eun-a.

702
01:01:05,244 --> 01:01:06,287
Mo Eun-a!

703
01:01:07,205 --> 01:01:08,039
Lepas.

704
01:01:08,956 --> 01:01:10,249
Awak patut ucap tahniah.

705
01:01:10,333 --> 01:01:12,085
Tetamu kita terkejut.

706
01:01:12,168 --> 01:01:13,628
Ambil bunga ini, masuk.

707
01:01:13,711 --> 01:01:15,463
Bagus sangat buat kerja dia.

708
01:01:19,759 --> 01:01:23,137
Tidakkah awak dah dewasa
nak marah pasal hubungan ayah awak?

709
01:01:24,305 --> 01:01:26,015
Fokus pada hidup sendirilah.

710
01:01:27,684 --> 01:01:28,851
Saya boleh carikan kerja.

711
01:01:31,729 --> 01:01:33,106
Tak jamin akan membantu.

712
01:02:30,913 --> 01:02:33,666
Ia cenderung berhenti
atau terbalik di cerun curam.

713
01:02:34,584 --> 01:02:36,461
Agihan berat tak seimbang?

714
01:02:36,544 --> 01:02:38,379
Kalau tukar rekaan dua tayar?

715
01:02:38,463 --> 01:02:39,881
<i>Awak sibuk?</i>

716
01:02:39,964 --> 01:02:41,174
<i>Di makmal profesor.</i>

717
01:02:41,257 --> 01:02:43,134
<i>Ini kelas siswazah,</i>

718
01:02:43,217 --> 01:02:45,511
<i>tapi pembantu pengajar beri masuk.</i>

719
01:02:45,595 --> 01:02:46,554
<i>Menarik juga.</i>

720
01:02:47,138 --> 01:02:49,932
<i>Macam sibuk. Habis pukul berapa?</i>

721
01:02:50,016 --> 01:02:53,603
<i>Ada apa? Kalau mustahak,</i>
<i>saya boleh telefon sekarang.</i>

722
01:02:53,686 --> 01:02:55,938
Awak patut ambil jurusan mengampu.

723
01:02:56,939 --> 01:02:59,233
Apalah. Sekejap lagi kita sambung.

724
01:02:59,317 --> 01:03:01,736
<i>- Tak apa. Sembang nanti.</i>
- Ya, profesor.

725
01:03:02,487 --> 01:03:04,906
Profesor suka piza <i>supreme.</i>

726
01:03:04,989 --> 01:03:07,200
- Boleh saya ke tandas?
- Pergilah.

727
01:03:08,534 --> 01:03:09,827
Profesor, silakan.

728
01:03:14,040 --> 01:03:15,500
<i>Awak tahu?</i>

729
01:03:16,000 --> 01:03:19,462
<i>Kita boleh nampak Namsan</i>
<i>dari mana-mana di Seoul.</i>

730
01:03:19,545 --> 01:03:22,882
<i>Mulai sekarang, nama awak Namsan.</i>

731
01:03:22,965 --> 01:03:24,175
<i>Yeon Namsan.</i>

732
01:03:26,636 --> 01:03:29,931
<i>Saya pula masih tersekat</i>
<i>dalam ketidakpastian.</i>

733
01:03:38,523 --> 01:03:39,607
<i>Awak di mana?</i>

734
01:03:40,691 --> 01:03:42,068
<i>Tanah lembap.</i>

735
01:03:42,151 --> 01:03:45,279
<i>Tak, saya di hentian bas.</i>

736
01:03:48,950 --> 01:03:51,786
TAE-SEO

737
01:03:58,292 --> 01:03:59,252
<i>Awak di Seoul, bukan?</i>

738
01:04:00,878 --> 01:04:03,172
<i>Masa merayau, saya nak beli solekan,</i>

739
01:04:03,256 --> 01:04:05,466
<i>kemudian makan mi.</i>

740
01:04:06,175 --> 01:04:08,052
<i>Awak ada urusan penting.</i>

741
01:04:08,135 --> 01:04:09,554
<i>Jangan bazirkan masa.</i>

742
01:04:09,637 --> 01:04:12,640
<i>Saya banyak masa, nanti saya singgah lagi.</i>

743
01:04:13,558 --> 01:04:15,309
<i>Jangan merepek.</i>

744
01:04:15,393 --> 01:04:17,311
<i>Kita bersama itu paling penting.</i>

745
01:04:24,110 --> 01:04:27,446
<i>Tae-seo, saya betul-betul nak jumpa awak.</i>

746
01:04:34,287 --> 01:04:35,246
<i>Saya datang.</i>

747
01:04:36,080 --> 01:04:37,415
<i>Awak tak tahu saya di mana.</i>

748
01:04:38,791 --> 01:04:39,625
<i>Tunggu.</i>

749
01:04:47,800 --> 01:04:48,968
<i>Satu stesen lagi.</i>

750
01:04:49,051 --> 01:04:49,886
<i>Sikit lagi.</i>

751
01:05:01,856 --> 01:05:03,316
STESEN GANGBYEON

752
01:05:13,659 --> 01:05:16,829
<i>Aku boleh dengar Yeon Tae-seo datang.</i>

753
01:05:27,506 --> 01:05:29,300
<i>Habis merayau.</i>

754
01:05:32,303 --> 01:05:35,222
STILL SHINING

755
01:06:01,165 --> 01:06:04,085
<i>Sebelum masuk tentera,</i>
<i>awak memang lalui waktu sukar.</i>

756
01:06:04,794 --> 01:06:06,337
<i>Saya benci perpisahan.</i>

757
01:06:07,254 --> 01:06:08,756
Dah 10 tahun saya lupa.

758
01:06:09,966 --> 01:06:11,300
<i>Hilang.</i>

759
01:06:11,384 --> 01:06:13,094
Eun-a…

760
01:06:13,177 --> 01:06:15,054
Awak tak dengar khabar dia, bukan?

761
01:06:15,763 --> 01:06:16,973
<i>Tak perlulah…</i>

762
01:06:18,265 --> 01:06:20,059
<i>risau dan runsing.</i>

763
01:06:20,142 --> 01:06:21,352
<i>Saya fikirkan awak.</i>

764
01:06:24,563 --> 01:06:27,274
<i>Saya harap dapat jumpa awak sekali.</i>

765
01:06:34,323 --> 01:06:36,325
Terjemahan sari kata oleh Hazleen Hamdan

